HTML is markup language - but, you can remember its as Sentactical language.
- Simple & declarative language or structre language.
- HTML lang make your website structre then its called structre lang.

Q. - Why HTML so popular ? 
=> HTML have large support in browser.
     
HTML Heading -
<h1> In h1 tag big heading </h1>
<h2> h2 for smaller heading than h1 </h2> 
*NOTE :-> But these is not correct only that h1 bigger & h2 smaller in header.

All tags in HTML have takes Importance
  - <h1>---Is a Heading---</h1> ==>  h1 means its CORE PART/Most important part of page includes all heading of website.
  - <h2>---Is a Subheading---</h2> ==> h2 is a second importance than h1.

All tags of HTML have different importance & these imporatance makes your (website)page structure.
  E.g. -
  <address></addresss> tag -> google know automatically its get address from structure & list it. without user extra effort for list it.

