=>
   ! + tab --> Basic structre

   E.g. -
      html tag ---> <!DOCTYPE html>
      - All html tags are in Case Insensitive E.g. HEAD or head similar
   HTML -
      1] --> <head></head>
      2] --> <body></body>

On web page, all whole page is html body part as a visual accpect.
2 parts are visuals in Head -
  1] Title
  2] Favicon

Meta Tags -
Q. - What is meta tags ?
=>
   E.g. - 
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   - Info about your document this can't write in page but, some server, botcrawl inform through it.
   - On page "smile" support we use --> <meta charset="UTF-16">

   name="viewport" content="width=device-width" 
   - After render page by default what zoom level show on page?
   
meta tags(elements) - RESOURCE
Google - meta tags in html Google

Google recommands on "developer.google" ==> all tags on this page.
https://developers.google.com/search/docs

In vs code -
meta: ==> emmet help in VS code for meta tags

*NOTE :- HTML - No show any error

E.g.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
      <meta charset="UTF-16">
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
      <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
      <h1>heading</h1>
      <footer>
            <address></address>
      </footer>
</body>
</html>
